    <item>
      <title>以色列官员对与哈马斯的停火谈判表示乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/israel-officials-optimistic-over-talks-with-hamas-on-gaza-hostages-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列高级官员表示，加沙停火谈判已取得进展，其中包括释放人质和巴勒斯坦囚犯，此举引起了极右翼部长的批评，他们威胁要推翻政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/israel-officials-optimistic-over-talks-with-hamas-on-gaza-hostages-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚央行向外汇局提供美元汇率为 1,101 奈拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/nigeria-central-bank-offers-dollars-at-1-101-naira-to-fx-bureaux</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据其网站上的一份声明，尼日利亚央行提出以 1,101 奈拉的汇率向西非国家货币兑换处运营商出售美元，同时仍在采取稳定当地货币的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/nigeria-central-bank-offers-dollars-at-1-101-naira-to-fx-bureaux</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:18:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普表示各州应设定堕胎限制和例外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/trump-says-states-should-set-abortion-limits-notes-exceptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，各州应该决定堕胎政策，避免在全国性禁令上采取立场，因为他正在努力解决民主党面临的一个激励性问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/trump-says-states-should-set-abortion-limits-notes-exceptions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:18:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么特朗普的社交媒体公司充斥着法律案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/why-trump-s-social-media-company-is-facing-lots-of-lawsuits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普新上市的社交媒体公司卷入了许多法律案件，其中大部分涉及帮助成立该公司并将其与公共实体合并的高管涉嫌不当行为——以及前总统本人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/why-trump-s-social-media-company-is-facing-lots-of-lawsuits</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士计划于六月中旬主办乌克兰和平计划会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/switzerland-aims-to-hold-a-ukraine-peace-conference-in-mid-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，瑞士计划于 6 月中旬主办乌克兰高级别和平会议，邀请 80 至 100 个国家参加，其中大部分来自所谓的南半球国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/switzerland-aims-to-hold-a-ukraine-peace-conference-in-mid-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 10:39:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称创新打造电动汽车成功，拒绝欧盟补贴调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/china-says-innovation-built-ev-success-rejects-eu-subsidy-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国商务部长在巴黎访问期间表示，中国汽车制造商在激烈的竞争中不断创新，在电动汽车领域实现了快速增长，并拒绝了欧盟对该行业补贴的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/china-says-innovation-built-ev-success-rejects-eu-subsidy-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 10:24:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
